elements.expression:
filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT HISTOGRAM(\"@timestamp\", INTERVAL 30 SECOND) as interval, 
  count(*) as count
  FROM \"log-generator-logrus*\"
  GROUP by interval
  ORDER BY interval DESC
  LIMIT 50"
| pointseries x="interval" y="count" size="count"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars="4" color="#FFFFFF" points="1" lines="0"} legend=false xaxis=true 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#BBBBBB" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render
